		<skos:definition xml:lang="en">a g-dependent continuant b g-depends on an independent continuant c at some time =Def for some time t (there inheres in c an s-dependent continuant which concretizes b at t)</skos:definition>
		<skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">generically depends on at some time</skos:prefLabel>
	</owl:ObjectProperty>
	
