		<rdfs:label>inoculum expansion in a rocker bag recipe process operation</rdfs:label>
		<skos:definition>Cultivation of cells in single-use rocker bags to scale up inoculum volume while maintaining cell viability and sterility, typically used before bioreactor inoculation.</skos:definition>
