		<rdfs:label>monoclonal antibody upstream recipe process stage</rdfs:label>
		<skos:definition>The initial phase of mAb production involving cell line selection, media optimization, seed expansion, and cultivation in bioreactors to produce the target protein.</skos:definition>
		<CMCO:hasBlaName>Upstream Manufacturing Process</CMCO:hasBlaName>
		<AnnotationVocabulary:acronym>MAb USP</AnnotationVocabulary:acronym>
	</owl:Class>
	
